==English==
===Etymology===
From [[w:Hermann von Fehling|Hermann von Fehling]] german chemist
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Fehling's solution'''
#{{chemistry}} an alkaline solution of [[copper sulphate]] which changes from blue to red in the presence of an [[aldehyde]] or a [[reducing sugar]]
